{"tid":1423170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"班狗有PPRB，抗爭嘅手足都要有隊公關組","createTime":"2019-08-06T13:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T02:20:13.000Z","uid":198822,"like":112,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f90ccb5423570a9a280f0d430b65ad2444ed22dc","tid":1423170,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"事緣近幾次發夢，成日見到有啲巴打上哂火，同路人/司機口角甚或動武。<br />\n呢啲畫面畀旁觀者見到，其實有啲不堪；畢竟我地係公義之師，能夠以理服人當然最好。<br />\n<br />\n小弟明白好多巴打係夢境中做緊實事，未必有心力應付口舌之爭。<br />\n但係我地要贏，就要贏埋呢場舌上戰。<br />\n如果每次有呢啲紛爭，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">就會有班專責嘴炮嘅巴絲趕到做pr show，有禮貌咁同受影響人士講句sorry，再解釋埋抗爭嘅焦點</span></strong></span></strong>；咁樣會唔會幫到手？<br />\n前線出力，唔夠勇猛嘅巴絲去現場各處出把口，各有各做。只有勝，不會敗！"},{"pid":"33d046b2c325ba01b09ede23526a9f1faf1b9382","tid":1423170,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35542d871658b09f47e091379793697f9c2e3d6","tid":1423170,"uid":282289,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"抗爭公共關係<del>科</del>組<br />\nResistance Public Relations <del>Branch</del> Section<br />\nRPRS<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3a19d7ba2a6e93db5ce0b6f5f6083ce31b482f","tid":1423170,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8836d472d81d3a16b6e6885e1888858c80a2cb3a","tid":1423170,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60540cce39035e2012eb6aeff7fa5a0462da7f5","tid":1423170,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:11:21.000Z","msg":"因住又比人話起大台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/an